@startuml
title Vectis Platform Package Diagram

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Development Workspace" {
  package "src" {
    package "website" as Website
    package "webapp" as Webapp
    package "backend" as Backend
    package "pi-camera" as PiCamera
    package "agent" as Agent
    package "shared" as Shared
  }

  package "cicd/serverless" as Serverless
}

database "Local SQLite Queue" as LocalQueue
database "App DB\nLocal Postgres / AWS RDS" as AppDb
folder "Frame Storage\nLocal FS / S3" as FrameStore

cloud "AWS Production" {
  package "Amazon ECS" {
    component "website service" as AwsWebsite
    component "webapp service" as AwsWebapp
    component "backend service" as AwsBackend
  }

  component "AWS Lambda\nimage-processing-worker" as ImageWorker
  database "Amazon RDS\nPostgreSQL" as Rds
  collections "Amazon S3\nimage bucket" as S3
  collections "Amazon ECR\ncontainer images" as Ecr
  component "AWS Secrets Manager" as Secrets
  component "Application Load Balancer" as Alb
}

cloud "Life2 Platform" {
  component "auth-service" as AuthService
}

node "Home LAN" {
  node "Raspberry Pi" {
    component "pi-camera service" as PiRuntime
    component "production agent" as ProdAgent
  }
}

component "Developer Machine" as DevMachine

Website ..> Shared : product messaging\nsample content
Webapp ..> Shared : types and seeded data
Backend ..> Shared : contracts and sample resources

Webapp --> Backend : REST /api/v1
Webapp --> AuthService : browser handoff\n/signIn + callback token
AuthService --> Webapp : redirect with Life2 JWT
Backend --> AuthService : shared JWT contract\nissuer/audience/secret
Agent --> PiCamera : pull HTTP MPEG-TS stream
Agent --> Backend : HTTPS uploads\npreview, motion, telemetry
Agent --> LocalQueue : persist outbound payloads\nand retry state
Backend --> AppDb : Prisma ORM\nmigrations + CRUD persistence
Backend --> FrameStore : persist filtered frames\nfor later processing
Serverless ..> AwsWebsite : deploy ECS service
Serverless ..> AwsWebapp : deploy ECS service
Serverless ..> AwsBackend : deploy ECS service
Serverless ..> ImageWorker : deploy Lambda
Serverless ..> Rds : provision and wire
Serverless ..> S3 : provision bucket and events
Serverless ..> Secrets : bind runtime secrets
Ecr --> AwsWebsite : container image
Ecr --> AwsWebapp : container image
Ecr --> AwsBackend : container image
Alb --> AwsWebsite : host routing\nvectis-sense.ai
Alb --> AwsWebapp : host routing\napp.vectis-sense.ai
Alb --> AwsBackend : host routing\napi.vectis-sense.ai
AwsBackend --> Rds : relational state
AwsBackend --> S3 : image metadata + object access
ImageWorker --> S3 : read new objects\nwrite derivatives
ImageWorker --> AwsBackend : emit processed metadata
Secrets --> AwsBackend : runtime secrets
Secrets --> ImageWorker : worker secrets
DevMachine --> PiRuntime : SSH deploy + LAN access
DevMachine --> ProdAgent : SSH deploy
ProdAgent --> PiRuntime : pull local stream
ProdAgent --> AwsBackend : upload telemetry\nand media metadata
ProdAgent --> S3 : upload image payloads

note bottom of Shared
Shared currently contains
TypeScript contracts and
resource types consumed by
the authenticated webapp
and backend.
end note

note right of AuthService
Life2 auth-service owns
the hosted sign-in UX and
issues Life2 JWTs used by
Vectis.
end note

note bottom of Serverless
Serverless Framework definitions
and helper scripts live under
/cicd/serverless.
end note

@enduml
